National treatment trends among older patients with T1-localized renal cell 
carcinoma.

Kim SP(1), Gross CP(2), Meropol N(3), Kutikov A(4), Smaldone MC(4), Shah ND(5), 
Yu JB(6), Psutka S(7), Kiechle J(8), Abouassaly R(8).

Author information:
(1)Urology Institute, Center of Outcomes and Health Care Quality, University 
Hospitals Cleveland Medical Center, Cleveland, OH; Seidman Cancer Center, 
