Cost-effectiveness of active surveillance versus hemithyroidectomy for 
micropapillary thyroid cancer.

Venkatesh S(1), Pasternak JD(2), Beninato T(1), Drake FT(1), Kluijfhout WP(1), 
Liu C(3), Gosnell JE(1), Shen WT(1), Clark OH(1), Duh QY(1), Suh I(4).

Author information:
(1)Endocrine Surgery Section, Department of Surgery, University of California, 
San Francisco, CA.
(2)Department of Surgery, University Health Network, Toronto, Ontario, Canada.
(3)Division of Endocrinology, Department of Medicine, University of California, 
