Physical activity as part of daily living: Moving beyond quantitative 
recommendations.

Silva KS(1), Garcia LM(2), Rabacow FM(3), de Rezende LF(3), de Sá TH(4).

Author information:
(1)Federal University of Santa Catarina Sports Center, Campus Universitário 
Reitor João David Ferreira Lima, Florianópolis, SC 88040-900, Brazil. Electronic 
address: kelly.samara@ufsc.br.
(2)Oswaldo Cruz Foundation, Avenida Brasil, 4365, Residência Oficial, Rio de 
Janeiro, RJ 21040-360, Brazil.
(3)Department of Preventive Medicine, University of São Paulo School of 
Medicine, Av. Dr. Arnaldo, 455, São Paulo, SP 01246-903, Brazil.
(4)University of São Paulo, School of Public Health, Av. Dr. Arnaldo, 715, São 
